word_mean_info__list.difference: 指恰恰就在此刻，一秒钟也没耽误。
主要用于美国英语，语气稍弱于at once，强调动作迅速。
常用词，指行动快，完成速度快。
口语中常用，语气强烈，指时间紧迫，一刻也不能耽误。
和soon同义，指动作发生或完成的速度之快。
指做完一件事后，立即就做另一件事，中间一般没有明显的时间间隔。

yingyinNormal.en: I can hear my butter, which is all melted together but you'll leave that to cool, because if you put a hot mixture on this, it will kill the yeast instantly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我能听到黄油的声音，正在融为一体，但是你得让它冷却，因为如果你把这么热的东西放在上面，就会立即把酵母杀死。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm hearing now that the president received at least one gunshot to the abdomen, possibly more, that he clutched his stomach, that he fell instantly to the ground, and there were screams, people panicking, that it has been very chaotic at that scene.
yingyinNormal.zh: 导播现在告诉我总统至少腹部中了一枪，也许不止，他紧捂腹部，立即倒地，现场尖叫连连，人群陷入恐慌，场面十分混乱。

yingyinNormal.en: Quite the contrary. Most women who meet me almost instantly ask for some alone time. Excuse me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 恰恰相反，大部分见到我的女人立刻就要求跟我独处，抱歉。

yingyinNormal.en: No, it's true. I forget things almost instantly. It runs in my family. At least, I think it does.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不,是真的 我几乎马上就会忘掉发生的事情。是家庭遗传, 至少,我是这么认为的

yingyinNormal.en: But when I first gazed upon you, you were instantly more precious to me than all the wonders of the ancient world.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可当我第一眼看见你，就瞬间感觉你比远古世界所有奇观都要珍贵。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb》

yingyinNormal.en: Here's proof. If I tell you I bread needs, you instantly know that my grammar is off and I should be saying I need bread.
yingyinNormal.zh: 以下就是证据，如果我跟你说 “我面包要”，你立刻知道我的文法错误，应该要说 “我要面包”。

yingyinNormal.en: I know this to be a scandalous falsehood, though not wishing to injure him by supposing it possible, I instantly set off to make my sentiments known.
yingyinNormal.zh: 虽然我明知这是无稽之谈，虽然我不会那样看不起他，相信他真会有这种事情，我还是当机立断决定上这来一次，把我的意思说给你听。

yingyinNormal.en: The amount of electricity he had in his body should have killed him instantly, but it didn't, which tells me that the heart damage isn't as bad as you think.
yingyinNormal.zh: 通过他身体的电流是足以致死的，但他活下来了，这说明他的心脏没有那么脆弱。

yingyinNormal.en: It breaks down instantly, disintegrates all the artificial barriers that we've created between each other government, nationality, black, brown, yellow, white, whatever color you are, and shows each other our hearts, our fears, our hopes and our dreams.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它能瞬间瓦解我们之间制造的所有人为的障碍，政府，国籍，黑色，棕色，黄色，白色，不管你是什么人种，它让我们分享内心，分享恐惧，分享希望，分享梦。
